SENATE CHAMBER
STATE OF OKLAHOMA DISPOSITION
FLOOR AMENDMENT No. ________
COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
(Date)
I move to amend Senate Bill No. 1341, page 2, line 3, by inserting after the period the following:
“No money from the Career Counselor Revolving Fund shall be expended by any entity that
supports or includes any sort of support for diversity, equity, and inclusion (DEI), transgenderism,
LGBTQ, or similar ideologies. Any career counselor promoting or encouraging DEI,
transgenderism, LGBTQ, or similar ideologies shall be removed for cause.”
